adaboost的训练误差为：ERR=分类错误的样本数总样本数=∑i=1NI(G(xi)≠yi)N
ERR = \frac{\text{分类错误的样本数}}{\text{总样本数}} = \frac{\sum_{i=1}^NI(G(x_i) \neq y_i)}{N}
ERR=​总样本数​​分类错误的样本数​​=​N​​∑​i=1​N​​I(G(x​i​​)≠y​i​​)​​
adaboost算法最终分类器的误差界为：ERR=1N∑i=1NI(G(xi)≠yi)1≤1N∑i=1Nexp(−yif(xi))2=∏mZm3=∏m=1M(2em(1−em))4=∏m=1M(21−4γm2)5≤exp(−2∑m=1Mγm2)6
\begin{aligned}
ERR = \frac{1}{N}\sum_{i=1}^NI(G(x_i) \neq y_i)   &&{1}
\le \frac{1}{N}\sum_{i=1}^N\exp(-y_if(x_i))    &&{2}
= \prod_mZ_m    &&{3}
= \prod_{m=1}^M(2\sqrt {e_m(1-e_m)})    &&{4}
= \prod_{m=1}^M(2\sqrt {1-4\gamma_m^2})    &&{5}
\le \exp(-2\sum_{m=1}^M\gamma_m^2)   &&{6}
\end{aligned}
​ERR=​N​​1​​​i=1​∑​N​​I(G(x​i​​)≠y​i​​)​​​​​​1≤​N​​1​​​i=1​∑​N​​exp(−y​i​​f(x​i​​))​​​​​​2=​m​∏​​Z​m​​​​​​​​3=​m=1​∏​M​​(2√​e​m​​(1−e​m​​)​​​)​​​​​​4=​m=1​∏​M​​(2√​1−4γ​m​2​​​​​)​​​​​​5≤exp(−2​m=1​∑​M​​γ​m​2​​)​​​​​​6​​
说明：
（1）：ERR的定义（2）:I(G(xi)≠yi)=I(G(xi)≠yi)+0
