y_if(x_i)\lt 0 \Rightarrow \exp(-y_if(x_i))\gt 1 = I(G(x_i) \neq y_i)
y​i​​f(x​i​​)0⇒exp(−y​i​​f(x​i​​))>1=I(G(x​i​​)≠y​i​​)
当G(xi)=yiG(x_i) = y_iG(x​i​​)=y​i​​时，yif(xi)>0⇒exp(−yif(xi))>1=I(G(xi)≠yi)>0
y_if(x_i)\gt 0 \Rightarrow \exp(-y_if(x_i))\gt 1 = I(G(x_i) \neq y_i) \gt 0
y​i​​f(x​i​​)>0⇒exp(−y​i​​f(x​i​​))>1=I(G(x​i​​)≠y​i​​)>0
